name: RECCO® LOCATOR SKI JACKET SKI COLLECTION
description:
Jacket made of windproof and water repellent technical fabric. Ergonomic design to allow freedom of movement.

- High collar chin protection. Helmet compatible hood.
- Long sleeves with adjustable cuffs with adhesive straps. Interior elastic cuffs with thumbholes.
- Underarm zippers for ventilation.
- Front pockets with waterproof zipper closure. Lift ticket pocket at sleeve.
- Multifunction interior pockets.
- Integrated RECCO® reflector: the RECCO® reflector is a small transponder without batteries that lets you be found by professional mountain rescue teams in case of an avalanche.
- Interior anti-snow skirt with silicone band that improves the garment’s fit.
- Printed logo detail.

Zara Athleticz.

name: EXPLORER BACKPACK
description:
Explorer style backpack. Soft construction. Made of technical fabric. Main compartment with drawstring and flap with sporty closure. Large central interior open pocket and two medium pockets at sides. Interior zipper to access main compartment. Two mesh pockets at sides and two straps to adjust the size of the backpack. Flap features two pockets with zipper closure. Back features two adjustable straps for carrying accessories like mats, jackets, etc. Handle and two adjustable, breathable shoulder straps. Ergonomic breathable back for more comfort during use. Removable band with two pockets with lower zipper closure. Adjustable chest strap with clip closure and whistle. Ideal for hiking. 

Zara Athleticz.

name: WINDPROOF AND WATERPROOF RECCO® TECHNOLOGY DOWN JACKET SKI COLLECTION
description:
Down puffer jacket made with 85% down and 15% feather fill with 750 fill power for heat insulation, allowing for thermal comfort practicing snowboard/ski activities in temperatures down to -18ºC (-0.4ºF). Fabric is double-layered wind- and waterproof with up to a 15,000 mm water column and combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing breathability. Heat-sealed seams that reinforce protection against snow and rain. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

High collar with polar fleece lining and hood. Long sleeves with elasticized cuffs. Sleeve pocket for lift ticket. Adjustable ventilation at underarms with hidden in-seam zip closure.

Interior pocket for cell phone. Front pockets with polar fleece interior lining and zip closure. Interior mesh pocket for gloves with glasses cleaner. 

Removable interior tail to keep out snow and adjustable hem with elastic straps to prevent cold from getting in. Front waterproof double runner zipper closure with adjustable ventilation panel. Seamless padding designed to reduce the amount of topstitching and avoid the entrance of wind and water. 

*For more information about RECCO® technology, please visit their website: https://recco.com

An elevated version of the classic bomber jacket that dispenses with the elastic hem to create a clean silhouette. The detachable hooded collar, the front horizontal topstitching, and the elastic cord at the hem with a toggle are highlighted in this garment of refined design with a high-low hem.

name: WINDPROOF AND WATERPROOF RECCO® TECHNOLOGY DOWN JACKET SKI COLLECTION
description:
Down puffer jacket made with 85% down and 15% feather fill with 750 fill power for heat insulation, allowing for thermal comfort for snowboarding/skiing. Double-layered wind- and waterproof fabric with up to a 24,000 mm water column and combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing 20,000g / m2 / 24h breathability. Heat-sealed seams that reinforce protection against snow and rain. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

High collar with interior hood with exterior adjustable elastic cords. Long sleeves with elasticized cuffs. Lift ticket pocket at sleeve with glasses cleaner. Interior cell phone pocket with compass. Front pockets with polar fleece interior lining and zip closure.

Removable interior tail to keep out snow and adjustable hem with elastic straps to prevent cold from getting in. Front waterproof zipper closure adjusts with double runner. Includes washing instructions inside.

*For more information about RECCO® technology, please visit their website: https://recco.com

Fabric is double-layered wind- and waterproof with up to a 15K water column and combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing breathability of 20,000g / m2 / 24h. Heat-sealed seams that reinforce protection against snow and rain. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

High collar with polar fleece lining for better warmth and elastic strap to secure scarf. Removable and adjustable faux fur hood with elastic drawstring. Long sleeves with interior cuffs and thumb holes. Sleeve pocket for lift ticket. Interior pocket for cell phone with glasses cleaner. 

Front pockets with polar fleece interior lining and zip closure. Back pocket for storing gloves. Adjustable waist with side flaps. Removable interior tail to keep out snow. Front waterproof zipper closure adjusts with double runner.

*For more information about RECCO® technology, please visit their website: https://recco.com

An eau de parfum dressed up with the warm and textural notes of precious saffron and coriander, bitter orange provides a fruity and colorful touch to the luminous floral bouquet. name: LOVE EXPLOSION SPECIAL EDITION EAU DE PARFUM 80 ML
description:
ZARA LOVE EXPLOSION SPECIAL EDITION EAU DE PARFUM 80 ML (2.71 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. A LIMITED EDITION fragrance that combines the captivating charm of Red Temptation with the elegance of Rose Gourmand, a luxurious fusion of bright rose and softening vanilla. With amber floral, fruity, and gourmand notes, the top notes of this fragrance include: bergamot, bitter orange, and peony. The middle notes are rose, praline, and amber, with base notes of moss, vanilla, and musk.

name: APPLEJUICE 90 ML (3.0 FL. OZ)
description:
ZARA APPLEJUICE EAU DE TOILETTE 90 ML (3.0 FL. OZ). 

APPLEJUICE unveils a fruity floral perfume, a lively and voluptuous fragrance. Effervescent notes of apple, orange, and pink grapefruit reveal a vibrant fresh top note. 
At its core, the fragrance highlights the sensuality and femininity of a natural floral bouquet (rose, jasmine, violet, and peony). 
The musky woody notes of cedar and sandalwood enhance the modern silhouette of the composition and add an enveloping touch.

name: SENSUAL VANILLA 30 ML
description:
ZARA SENSUAL VANILLA EDP 30 ML (1.0 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. An indulgent floral amber scent with a heart of warm vanilla mocha. This luxurious fragrance combines rich florals with the comfort of creamy vanilla. 
Top notes: bergamot, sugary berries, Orpur France lavandin, rose. 
Middle notes: jasmine, lily, apple blossom, Orpur Madagascar vanilla. 
Base notes: Orpur vanilla, heliotrope, amber, musk, sandalwood.

name: ANGELIC VANILLA 30 ML
description:
ZARA ANGELIC VANILLA EDP 30 ML (1.0 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. A floral musk with an addictive blend of vanilla and tonka bean. This ethereal fragrance combines delicate florals with a sweet and creamy base, leaving a captivating impression. 
Top notes: bergamot, almond blossom. 
Middle notes: rose, rice, myrrh. 
Base notes: tonka bean, liquid musk, vanilla beans, velvety wood.

name: SENSUAL VANILLA 80 ML
description:
ZARA SENSUAL VANILLA EDP 80 ML (2.71 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. An indulgent floral amber scent with a heart of warm vanilla mocha. This luxurious fragrance combines rich florals with the comfort of creamy vanilla. 
Top notes: bergamot, sugary berries, Orpur France lavandin, rose. 
Middle notes: jasmine, lily, apple blossom, Orpur Madagascar vanilla. 
Base notes: Orpur vanilla, heliotrope, amber, musk, sandalwood.

name: ANGELIC VANILLA 80 ML
description:
ZARA ANGELIC VANILLA EDP 80 ML (2.71 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. A floral musk with an addictive blend of vanilla and tonka bean. This ethereal fragrance combines delicate florals with a sweet and creamy base, leaving a captivating impression. Top notes: bergamot, almond blossom. Middle notes: rose, rice, myrrh. Base notes: tonka bean, liquid musk, vanilla beans, velvety wood.

name: APPLEJUICE 30 ML
description:
ZARA APPLEJUICE EAU DE TOILETTE 30 ML (1.0 FL. OZ). 

APPLEJUICE unveils a fruity floral perfume, a lively and voluptuous fragrance. Effervescent notes of apple, orange, and pink grapefruit reveal a vibrant fresh top note. At its core, the fragrance highlights the sensuality and femininity of a natural floral bouquet (rose, jasmine, violet, and peony). The musky woody notes of cedar and sandalwood enhance the modern silhouette of the composition and add an enveloping touch.

name: BALADE DE FIGUIER 100 ML
description:
ZARA SILENT FLOWERS BALADE DE FIGUIER PARFUM 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Perfume. A sunny escape in an orchard of luminous fig trees in Provence. BALADE DE FIGUIER evokes the blossoms of a fig tree, composed of bright citric blends with the crispy green effect of petitgrain. A woody trail with vetiver and white musk touches fulfill the evocation of this Mediterranean universe. 

Top notes: grapefruit / fig leaf / mandarin.
Middle notes: petitgrain / fig milk / iris / tobacco leaf.
Base notes: benjui / muscone / Haiti vetiver.

A COLLECTION CREATED BY JO MALONE CBE, FOUNDER OF JO LOVES.

name: TOPSTITCHED BUCKET BAG
description:
Bucket bag with contrasting topstitching. Handle and two adjustable and removable crossbody straps. Magnetic closure. 

Height x Length x Width: 8.3 x 8 x 4.8 inches (21 x 20.3 x 12.3 cm)

name: PEONY 90 ML
description:
ZARA PEONY EDP 90 ML (3.0 FL. OZ). 

Bright and delicate eau de parfum. The scent of peony mixes the flavor of sun-bathed pear and black currant with the softness of an elegant floral bouquet. A delightful fruit explosion of pear and black currant provide a luminous and natural touch to the top notes. The middle focuses all the passion of peony. A fresh and happy flower accompanied by an elegant bouquet of rose - gardenia and iris. A creamy accord of tonka bean - black vanilla, and praline envelop the woody amber character with a deliciously addictive signature.

name: PÉTALE D'AMBRE 100 ML
description:
ZARA SILENT FLOWERS PÉTALE D'AMBRE PARFUM 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ). 

Perfume. PÉTALE D’AMBRE is a perfume that inspires curiosity and invites us on a new olfactory voyage. An amber flower that combines the aromatic floral facets of lavender with the magnetism of an amber note. Not too delicate and not too wild, the fragrance is vibrant and hypnotic at the same time. 

Top notes: essence of bergamot / essence of hint of lemon. 
Middle notes: essence of lavender diva / essence of walnut / lily of the valley / rockrose. 
Base notes: cashmere wood / essence of patchouli / ambergris. 

A COLLECTION CREATED BY JO MALONE CBE, FOUNDER OF JO LOVES.

name: BRÛLANTE VIOLETTE 100 ML
description:
ZARA SILENT FLOWERS BRÛLANTE VIOLETTE PARFUM 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Perfume. BRÛLANTE VIOLETTE celebrates the enchanting violet, a flower full of light. This bouquet of violets, freshened by the juicy fruity character of raspberry, blends with the magnetism of iris and the sophistication of moss. A carnal and intense elixir of feminine sensuality. 

Top notes: magnolia / rosebud firabs / elemi resin.
Middle notes: violet leaf / iris / raspberry. 
Base notes: cedar wood / moss / white musk. 

A COLLECTION CREATED BY JO MALONE CBE, FOUNDER OF JO LOVES.

name: ROMANCE D’IRIS 100 ML
description:
ZARA SILENT FLOWERS ROMANCE D’IRIS PARFUM 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Perfume. Precious and elusive, ROMANCE D’IRIS elicits a sensual and romantic interpretation of the iris flower. This fragrance was conceived as a blossomy love story in Florence. At the heart, iris (the flower of Love) seduces us with its powdery scent, hypnotic, and textured. A sensual overdose of heliotrope, rice, and white musk wrap around the composition with a velvet and immersive caress. 

Top notes: bergamot / rice.
Middle notes: iris flower / Florentine iris / violet. 
Base notes: captive white musk / vetiver / heliotrope. 

A COLLECTION CREATED BY JO MALONE CBE, FOUNDER OF JO LOVES.

name: PARFAIT D´ORCHIDÉE 100 ML
description:
ZARA SILENT FLOWERS PARFAIT D’ORCHIDÉE PARFUM 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Perfume. PARFAIT D’ORCHIDÉE captures the essence of a summer’s day on the Australian coast. The bright aroma of vanilla orchid blossom wrapped in a bouquet of velveted flowers and vibrant spices will carry you away on a voyage to lush, glistening beaches. Ambergris adds a rich texture, like the last warm rays of a summer’s day. 

Top notes: SFE incense / jasmine petals / ginger.
Middle notes: iris / benjui siam resin.
Base notes: vanilla / white musk / ambergris. 

A COLLECTION CREATED BY JO MALONE CBE, FOUNDER OF JO LOVES.

description:
Technical pants with waterproof fabric up to a 15,000 mm water column and triple layered that combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing breathability. 4-way stretch fabric that guarantees good freedom of movement and comfort. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

High waist with adjustable side tongues. Back padded waist for increased comfort and protection. Front ring on loop to hang gloves. Front pockets with waterproof zippers. Polar fleece lined interior. Flared legs adjustable with zip and longer back to accommodate ski boots. Interior elastic cuffs with hook to attach to footwear and keep out snow and cold. Front closure with zipper, metal hook, and adhesive strap with snap button.

*For more information about RECCO® technology, please visit their website: https://recco.com

name: WINDPROOF AND WATERPROOF RECCO® TECHNOLOGY FLARED SNOW OVERALLS SKI COLLECTION
description:
Technical overalls with waterproof fabric up to a 20,000 mm water column and triple layered that combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing breathability of 10,000g / m2 / 24h. 4-way stretch fabric with fitted silhouette that guarantee good freedom of movement and comfort. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

Wide straps and adjustable elastic cords. Back quilted panel with Airtex foam for better protection and breathability. Front pockets with waterproof zippers. Adjustable waist with side flaps. Polar fleece lined interior. Adjustable bell bottoms with zipper and inner patch to avoid wear and tear. Hem is longer in back to accommodate ski boots. Interior elastic cuffs to tuck into footwear and keep out snow and cold. Front waterproof zipper closure.

*For more information about RECCO® technology, please visit their website: https://recco.com

name: WINDPROOF AND WATERPROOF RECCO® TECHNOLOGY SKI COLLECTION JUMPSUIT
description:
Technical jumpsuit with waterproof fabric up to a 20,000 mm water column and triple layered that combines an exterior shell with an interior membrane that prevents water penetration but allows air through, providing breathability of 10,000g / m2 / 24h. 4-way stretch fabric with fitted silhouette that guarantee good freedom of movement and comfort. Equipped with RECCO®* technology to help rescue professionals find you in case of an accident, avalanche, or getting lost in difficult-to-reach areas.

High collar and long sleeves with lift ticket pocket. Fixed stretch belt with loops and clip closure. Upper pocket for mobile and front pockets with waterproof zippers. Front ring on loop to hang gloves. Polar fleece lined interior. Adjustable bell bottoms with zipper and inner patch to avoid wear and tear. Hem is longer in back to accommodate ski boots. Interior elastic cuffs with hook to tuck into footwear and keep out snow and cold. Front waterproof zipper closure.

name: GO FRUITY 100 ML
description:
ZARA GO FRUITY GLITTER EDP 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Eau de toilette that brings a sparkling femininity through a duo of delicious fruits where peach and apple mingle with a sublime bouquet of roses and iris flowers. The vanilla notes offer a final touch of sensuality, making the fragrance irresistible.

name: GOLDEN DECADE WINTER 80 ML
description:
ZARA GOLDEN DECADE WINTER EDP 80 ML (2.7 FL. OZ).

Eau de parfum. An addictive dreaminess that opens with the freshness of mandarin, bergamot, and orange blossom, making way to a woody, floral intensity that works with incense, jasmine, and lavender. Extremely sophisticated and sexy finish. 
Smelling notes: mandarin, bergamot, orange blossom, incense, jasmine, lavender, black vanilla, Tonka bean, vetiver, amber, musk. 
Intense.
A warm and hypnotic fragrance that stays on the skin all day long.

name: FEMME GLITTER 100 ML
description:
ZARA FEMME GLITTER EDP 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ).

Eau de toilette. Frangipani flower and peony, along with subtle hints of bergamot, open up the fragrance to create a vibrant sensation of surprising juiciness. At the heart, the seductive and powdery facets of orchid and heliotrope blend into the addictive creaminess of a vanilla and tonka bean accord. The velvety base of white musk and warm woody notes gives it a tactile and delicate character, enveloping the senses like an intense embrace.

name: FIELDS AT NIGHTFALL 100 ML
description:
ZARA FIELDS AT NIGHTFALL EDP 100 ML (3.4 FL. OZ) 

Amber eau de parfum with notes of praline, jasmine, and sandalwood.An elegant and feminine fragrance.

Eau de toilette. A fun and bold feminine fragrance with sweet floral accents of rose, jasmine, and orchid wrapped in the warmth of vanilla, woody notes, and amber. A seductive, addictive, and irresistible fragrance.
